  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0ddd \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca 6 \u0daf\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Litro gas is not available until the 6th",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of Litro Gas told 'Lankadeepa' that it will not be able to supply domestic gas until July 6.",
        "He said two ships of 3,500 metric tons each of gas imported by Litro were due to arrive between July 5 and 12 and the 6th resumption could begin if the ships arrived on time.",
        "The domestic gas supply to Litro was suspended on the 4th of this month due to lack of gas stocks and the domestic gas supply has not been maintained for 22 days.",
        "Long queues of gas cylinders can still be seen near gas outlets during those 22 days, even though gas distribution has stopped."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "6th",
          "label": "ORDINAL"
        }
      ],
